{"tid":553696,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"阿爺自身難保啦仲指意北水落黎掃港股?","createTime":"2018-02-07T17:21:48.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-09T06:29:04.000Z","uid":90595,"like":25,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"d8fff4af4d0d91e19fcadb50fbb34bc438fa7cb8","tid":553696,"uid":90595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T17:21:48.000Z","msg":"前日點解北水托得住個市？<br />\n<br />\n係因為<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">阿爺出口術</span></span>，要求證券商唔好即刻斬客戶倉，結果市場因中央出手維穩而情緒亢奮，令A股反升，港股亦都由跌800幾反彈番跌300幾。<br />\n<br />\n呢單新聞，大陸好多媒體都廣泛報導。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">Google 連結：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><a href=\"https://www.google.com.hk/search?q=%E8%A7%B8%E5%8F%8A%E5%B9%B3%E5%80%89%E7%B7%9A%EF%BC%8C%E8%AD%89%E5%88%B8%E5%85%AC%E5%8F%B8%E4%B9%9F%E4%B8%8D%E6%9C%83%E7%AB%8B%E5%88%BB%E5%9F%B7%E8%A1%8C%E8%99%95%E7%BD%AE&amp;oq=%E8%A7%B8%E5%8F%8A%E5%B9%B3%E5%80%89%E7%B7%9A%EF%BC%8C%E8%AD%89%E5%88%B8%E5%85%AC%E5%8F%B8%E4%B9%9F%E4%B8%8D%E6%9C%83%E7%AB%8B%E5%88%BB%E5%9F%B7%E8%A1%8C%E8%99%95%E7%BD%AE&amp;aqs=chrome..69i57&amp;sourceid=chrome&amp;ie=UTF-8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com.hk%2Fsearch%3Fq%3D%25E8%25A7%25B8%25E5%258F%258A%25E5%25B9%25B3%25E5%2580%2589%25E7%25B7%259A%25EF%25BC%258C%25E8%25AD%2589%25E5%2588%25B8%25E5%2585%25AC%25E5%258F%25B8%25E4%25B9%259F%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%259C%2583%25E7%25AB%258B%25E5%2588%25BB%25E5%259F%25B7%25E8%25A1%258C%25E8%2599%2595%25E7%25BD%25AE%26oq%3D%25E8%25A7%25B8%25E5%258F%258A%25E5%25B9%25B3%25E5%2580%2589%25E7%25B7%259A%25EF%25BC%258C%25E8%25AD%2589%25E5%2588%25B8%25E5%2585%25AC%25E5%258F%25B8%25E4%25B9%259F%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%259C%2583%25E7%25AB%258B%25E5%2588%25BB%25E5%259F%25B7%25E8%25A1%258C%25E8%2599%2595%25E7%25BD%25AE%26aqs%3Dchrome..69i57%26sourceid%3Dchrome%26ie%3DUTF-8&d=%2BJcdb9KI6Gg6TMKANRyj0wtTNu1qqkxUxYmVHECffP4%3D&h=7fa93feb\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com.hk/search?q=%E8%A7%B8%E5%8F%8A%E5%B9%B3%E5%80%89%E7%B7%9A%EF%BC%8C%E8%AD%89%E5%88%B8%E5%85%AC%E5%8F%B8%E4%B9%9F%E4%B8%8D%E6%9C%83%E7%AB%8B%E5%88%BB%E5%9F%B7%E8%A1%8C%E8%99%95%E7%BD%AE&amp;oq=%E8%A7%B8%E5%8F%8A%E5%B9%B3%E5%80%89%E7%B7%9A%EF%BC%8C%E8%AD%89%E5%88%B8%E5%85%AC%E5%8F%B8%E4%B9%9F%E4%B8%8D%E6%9C%83%E7%AB%8B%E5%88%BB%E5%9F%B7%E8%A1%8C%E8%99%95%E7%BD%AE&amp;aqs=chrome..69i57&amp;sourceid=chrome&amp;ie=UTF-8</a></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.chinatimes.com/newspapers/20180206000252-260203\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.chinatimes.com%2Fnewspapers%2F20180206000252-260203&d=%2BJcdb9KI6Gg6TMKANRyj0wtTNu1qqkxUxYmVHECffP4%3D&h=bd22fa6d\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.chinatimes.com/newspapers/20180206000252-260203</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">新浪財經昨（5）日引述消息人士透露，證監會上周起便要求券商機構在股票質押回購業務上要維護市場穩定，如果股價因短期大幅波動而觸及平倉線，要求證券公司不要立刻執行處置，而應與客戶積極溝通，要求客戶補充擔保品。且擔保品不限於股票、現金等金融資產，包括房地產、土地等也可以作為擔保品。<br />\n<br />\n東方財富網分析，上周A股之所以急挫，主要是官方要求降槓桿防風險，並傳出將推出新資產管理辦法，因此拉響「股權質押」的警報，多家個股在盤中頻現閃崩。由於部分個股股價已跌至平倉線，為避免機構大舉平倉導致大盤雪上加霜，證監會因此宣布相關維穩措施。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n跟住琴日美股同環球都反彈，但點解最後turn out係唯獨是大陸跌到呀媽都唔認得，而且內銀特別沽壓嚴重？今日A股表現：<br />\n601288\t農業銀行\t\t4.46\t-0.25\t-5.31%\t5.174B\t<br />\n600036\t招商銀行\t\t32.39\t-2.23\t-6.44%\t4.982B\t<br />\n601988\t中國銀行\t\t4.59\t-0.17\t-3.57%\t3.092B<br />\n601939\t建設銀行\t\t8.84\t-0.56\t-5.96%\t3.002B<br />\n<br />\n兩大催命符，就係樂視同海航欠債同資金鏈問題。相信大家都知海航有7間子公司已經停晒牌。今日仲爆出海航其中一間子公司連信託基金條數都無法如期找付。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.secretchina.com/news/b5/2018/02/07/849362.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.secretchina.com%2Fnews%2Fb5%2F2018%2F02%2F07%2F849362.html&d=%2BJcdb9KI6Gg6TMKANRyj0wtTNu1qqkxUxYmVHECffP4%3D&h=947a580f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.secretchina.com/news/b5/2018/02/07/849362.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">Google 連結：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><a href=\"https://www.google.com.hk/search?q=%E6%B5%B7%E8%88%AA+%E7%84%A1%E6%B3%95%E5%85%8C%E4%BB%98&amp;source=lnms&amp;tbm=nws&amp;sa=X&amp;ved=0ahUKEwj-4tzIo5TZAhXHE7wKHbvvBnwQ_AUICigB&amp;biw=1920&amp;bih=974\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com.hk%2Fsearch%3Fq%3D%25E6%25B5%25B7%25E8%2588%25AA%2B%25E7%2584%25A1%25E6%25B3%2595%25E5%2585%258C%25E4%25BB%2598%26source%3Dlnms%26tbm%3Dnws%26sa%3DX%26ved%3D0ahUKEwj-4tzIo5TZAhXHE7wKHbvvBnwQ_AUICigB%26biw%3D1920%26bih%3D974&d=%2BJcdb9KI6Gg6TMKANRyj0wtTNu1qqkxUxYmVHECffP4%3D&h=31d9e7ab\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com.hk/search?q=%E6%B5%B7%E8%88%AA+%E7%84%A1%E6%B3%95%E5%85%8C%E4%BB%98&amp;source=lnms&amp;tbm=nws&amp;sa=X&amp;ved=0ahUKEwj-4tzIo5TZAhXHE7wKHbvvBnwQ_AUICigB&amp;biw=1920&amp;bih=974</a></span></span><br />\n<br />\n大陸自身難保啦，仲指意北水落黎救香港？趁價高抽錢走番去救A股，搞到香港今日跌咁多呀！<br />\n<br />\n最後就係，外資大行睇法。<br />\n高盛：中資股再回調5%-10%則非常有吸引力 <span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">(<a href=\"http://sina.com.hk/news/article/20180207/2/70/2/%E9%AB%98%E7%9B%9B-%E4%B8%AD%E8%B3%87%E8%82%A1%E5%86%8D%E5%9B%9E%E8%AA%BF5-10%E5%89%87%E9%9D%9E%E5%B8%B8%E6%9C%89%E5%90%B8%E5%BC%95%E5%8A%9B-8482509.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fsina.com.hk%2Fnews%2Farticle%2F20180207%2F2%2F70%2F2%2F%25E9%25AB%2598%25E7%259B%259B-%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E8%25B3%2587%25E8%2582%25A1%25E5%2586%258D%25E5%259B%259E%25E8%25AA%25BF5-10%25E5%2589%2587%25E9%259D%259E%25E5%25B8%25B8%25E6%259C%2589%25E5%2590%25B8%25E5%25BC%2595%25E5%258A%259B-8482509.html&d=%2BJcdb9KI6Gg6TMKANRyj0wtTNu1qqkxUxYmVHECffP4%3D&h=bd200b2e\" target=\"_blank\">http://sina.com.hk/news/article/20180207/2/70/2/%E9%AB%98%E7%9B%9B-%E4%B8%AD%E8%B3%87%E8%82%A1%E5%86%8D%E5%9B%9E%E8%AA%BF5-10%E5%89%87%E9%9D%9E%E5%B8%B8%E6%9C%89%E5%90%B8%E5%BC%95%E5%8A%9B-8482509.html</a>)</span><br />\n人話解讀：唔跌到佢老母西咁都唔會買住<br />\n<br />\n大摩：估計港股有機會跌至28350點才喘定，恆指已跌破穿該行今年基本目標31500點，股市要穩定下來，需要滿足以下至少兩項條件，包括恆指跌至28350點至30000點，回復至較佳風險回報水平<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><a href=\"https://www.xcnnews.com/cj/3257787.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.xcnnews.com%2Fcj%2F3257787.html&d=%2BJcdb9KI6Gg6TMKANRyj0wtTNu1qqkxUxYmVHECffP4%3D&h=3c7b4387\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.xcnnews.com/cj/3257787.html</a></span><br />\n人話解讀：短期睇28350，而家買冇著數<br />\n<br />\n瑞信：雖然港股出現調整，但仍高於今年28000點的目標，由於估值並非太便宜，相信大市仍有下跌空間。<br />\n人話解讀：仲有排你睇<br />\n[url]<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><a href=\"https://www.news.now.com/home/finance/player?newsId=253280\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.news.now.com%2Fhome%2Ffinance%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D253280&d=%2BJcdb9KI6Gg6TMKANRyj0wtTNu1qqkxUxYmVHECffP4%3D&h=f4c98af8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.news.now.com%2Fhome%2Ffinance%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D253280&h=bb9c4d67\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.news.now.com/home/finance/player?newsId=253280</a></span>[/url]<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">如果今晚美股升，聽朝高開好走貨啦，星期四五都一定睇跌呀。</span></span>"},{"pid":"e9e120146952c1f30ef9f9c8ce0f74a79808069c","tid":553696,"uid":56743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T17:31:11.000Z","msg":"leave name"},{"pid":"ba39f8758262753d433f1a49a0aa0f382919cfa0","tid":553696,"uid":18912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T17:39:59.000Z","msg":"wu ar"},{"pid":"cf7ab7bcc723a4af65383089fd3883b96dafedfe","tid":553696,"uid":144774,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T17:48:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4623a1082f25664a1374f29f089d43fca6c5cbae","tid":553696,"uid":90601,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T17:57:17.000Z","msg":"雖然個人覺得北水唔會咁簡單玩完 or 只係海航+樂視就拉得爆<br />\n但經過今日一役 真心覺得依家北水企唔穩 全世界點升都無用 HSI都係收皮"},{"pid":"22f5c5866cff4ce09777798e2768956e0e3f8cf0","tid":553696,"uid":88032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T18:53:59.000Z","msg":"去槓杆嘛<br />\n陣痛在所難免"},{"